---
const check = `<svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M2.5 8.5 L6 12 L13.5 4.5"></path></svg>`;
---

<section id="servicios" class="py-24 md:py-32 px-6">
  <div class="text-center max-w-[760px] mx-auto mb-16">
    <span class="reveal block text-[12px] font-bold tracking-[3px] uppercase text-accent mb-4">Servicios</span>
    <h2 class="reveal font-bold uppercase text-white" style="--stagger:1; font-size:clamp(2.4rem,5vw,60px); line-height:1.2; letter-spacing:1.2px;">¿Qué necesita tu negocio?</h2>
    <p class="reveal mt-4 font-light text-white/60 leading-relaxed max-w-[560px] mx-auto" style="--stagger:2;">Cada proyecto es diferente. Elegí el tipo de solución y coordinamos una cotización a tu medida, sin costo.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="plans-list max-w-[1120px] mx-auto mt-16 border-t border-white/10">

    <article class="plan-row reveal" style="--stagger:0;">
      <div class="plan-idx text-[13px] font-bold tracking-[1.5px] text-accent/60 pt-2">01</div>
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 flex-wrap">
          <h3 class="plan-title">Página Web</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[14px] font-light leading-[1.65] text-white/55 max-w-[320px]">Presencia profesional en internet para tu empresa o negocio.</p>
      </div>
      <ul class="features pt-1.5 grid gap-3 list-none">
        <li class="flex gap-2.5 items-start text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-white/65"><span class="text-accent mt-0.5"><Fragment set:html={check} /></span><span>Diseño personalizado</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-2.5 items-start text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-white/65"><span class="text-accent mt-0.5"><Fragment set:html={check} /></span><span>Adaptada a celular y computadora</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-2.5 items-start text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-white/65"><span class="text-accent mt-0.5"><Fragment set:html={check} /></span><span>Optimizada para buscadores (SEO)</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-2.5 items-start text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-white/65"><span class="text-accent mt-0.5"><Fragment set:html={check} /></span><span>Dominio y hosting incluido el primer año</span></li>
      </ul>
      <div class="price-cell">
        <div class="text-accent font-bold" style="font-size:clamp(30px,2.6vw,38px); letter-spacing:0.5px; line-height:1;">Desde $800</div>
        <div class="mt-2 text-[13px] font-light text-white/45">pago único</div>
        <a href="#contacto" class="ghost-button mt-6 !py-3.5 !px-6 !text-[12px] !border-white/30">Cotizar página web</a>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="plan-row featured reveal" style="--stagger:1;">
      <div class="plan-idx text-[13px] font-bold tracking-[1.5px] text-accent/60 pt-2">02</div>
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 flex-wrap">
          <h3 class="plan-title">Sistema Web</h3>
          <span class="bg-accent text-white rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[1px] whitespace-nowrap">Más solicitado</span>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[14px] font-light leading-[1.65] text-white/55 max-w-[320px]">Automatizá procesos y gestioná tu negocio desde cualquier lugar.</p>
      </div>
      <ul class="features pt-1.5 grid gap-3 list-none">
        <li class="flex gap-2.5 items-start text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-white/65"><span class="text-accent mt-0.5"><Fragment set:html={check} /></span><span>Desarrollo a medida según tu operación</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-2.5 items-start text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-white/65"><span class="text-accent mt-0.5"><Fragment set:html={check} /></span><span>Panel de administración</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-2.5 items-start text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-white/65"><span class="text-accent mt-0.5"><Fragment set:html={check} /></span><span>Control de usuarios y roles</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-2.5 items-start text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-white/65"><span class="text-accent mt-0.5"><Fragment set:html={check} /></span><span>Integración con tu página web si la necesitás</span></li>
      </ul>
      <div class="price-cell">
        <div class="text-accent font-bold" style="font-size:clamp(30px,2.6vw,38px); letter-spacing:0.5px; line-height:1;">Desde $2,000</div>
        <div class="mt-2 text-[13px] font-light text-white/45">pago único</div>
        <a href="#contacto" class="filled-button mt-6 !py-3.5 !px-6 !text-[12px]">Cotizar sistema</a>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="plan-row reveal" style="--stagger:2;">
      <div class="plan-idx text-[13px] font-bold tracking-[1.5px] text-accent/60 pt-2">03</div>
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 flex-wrap">
          <h3 class="plan-title">Automatizaciones</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[14px] font-light leading-[1.65] text-white/55 max-w-[320px]">Ahorrá tiempo eliminando tareas repetitivas con flujos automáticos.</p>
      </div>
      <ul class="features pt-1.5 grid gap-3 list-none">
        <li class="flex gap-2.5 items-start text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-white/65"><span class="text-accent mt-0.5"><Fragment set:html={check} /></span><span>Diagnóstico de procesos automatizables</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-2.5 items-start text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-white/65"><span class="text-accent mt-0.5"><Fragment set:html={check} /></span><span>Integración con herramientas que ya usás</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-2.5 items-start text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-white/65"><span class="text-accent mt-0.5"><Fragment set:html={check} /></span><span>Reducción de errores manuales</span></li>
        <li class="flex gap-2.5 items-start text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-white/65"><span class="text-accent mt-0.5"><Fragment set:html={check} /></span><span>Soporte post-implementación</span></li>
      </ul>
      <div class="price-cell">
        <div class="text-accent font-bold" style="font-size:clamp(30px,2.6vw,38px); letter-spacing:0.5px; line-height:1;">Desde $500</div>
        <div class="mt-2 text-[13px] font-light text-white/45">pago único</div>
        <a href="#contacto" class="ghost-button mt-6 !py-3.5 !px-6 !text-[12px] !border-white/30">Cotizar automatización</a>
      </div>
    </article>

  </div>

  <div class="reveal text-center mt-12" style="--stagger:3;">
    <p class="text-[14px] font-light text-white/50 mb-6">¿No sabés cuál necesitás? Escribinos y te ayudamos a decidir sin compromiso.</p>
    <a href="#contacto" class="ghost-button">Hablar con nosotros</a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .plan-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
    padding: 48px 16px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
    align-items: start;
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
  }
  .plan-row:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); }
  .plan-row.featured { box-shadow: inset 3px 0 0 #01c38e; }

  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .plan-row {
      grid-template-columns: 52px 1.15fr 1fr auto;
      gap: 48px;
      padding: 56px 16px;
    }
    .price-cell { align-items: flex-end; text-align: right; min-width: 230px; }
  }

  .plan-title {
    font-size: clamp(22px, 2.2vw, 28px);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1.4px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .price-cell {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
</style>
